					<Body><![CDATA[// Assign triage level (1–5). 1 = most urgent.
triageLevel = uniform_discr(1, 5);


// Store event in treatment history
if (treatmentHistory != null) {
    treatmentHistory.add("Triage assigned = " + triageLevel);
}]]></Body>
